{
  "page": "Arbor Queen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:ArborQueen_Lukasz_Jaskolski.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/ArborQueen_Lukasz_Jaskolski.png/400px-ArborQueen_Lukasz_Jaskolski.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"260\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/ArborQueen_Lukasz_Jaskolski.png/600px-ArborQueen_Lukasz_Jaskolski.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/ArborQueen_Lukasz_Jaskolski.png/800px-ArborQueen_Lukasz_Jaskolski.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:ArborQueen_Lukasz_Jaskolski.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <i>Arbor Queen</i> - by Tomasz Jedruszek. © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>The <i><b>Arbor Queen</b></i> is a galleas owned by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Paxter_Redwyne\" title=\"Paxter Redwyne\">Paxter Redwyne</a> and is part of the <a href=\"/index.php/Redwyne_fleet\" title=\"Redwyne fleet\">Redwyne fleet</a>. She is five times as large as the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Blackbird\" title=\"Blackbird\">Blackbird</a></i>, the largest ship that belongs to the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>. It has three large burgundy sails and multiple banks of oars painted white and gold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arbor_Queen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a> once travelled on the <i>Arbor Queen</i>, when he sailed from <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a> to become a <a href=\"/index.php/Page\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Page\">page</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arbor_Queen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Samwell II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403155040\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.022 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.043 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 163/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8593/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 732/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 44/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursio